object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct subrogation.SystemId, 
subrogation.ParentId, 
subrogation.CMMContainer, 
subrogation.Id, 
subrogation.StatusCd, 
subrogation.Description, 
subrogation.SubrogationStatusCd, 
subrogation.StatuteDt, 
subrogation.OpenedDt, 
subrogation.ClosedDt,
 subrogation.DeductibleWaivedInd,
 subrogation.SubrogationProviderRef,
 subrogation.InstallmentPaymentInd,
 subrogation.ResponsiblePartyLiabilityPct,
 subrogation.RespPartyPreferDeliveryMethod, 
 subrogation.RespOwnerPreferDeliveryMethod,
 subrogation.InstallmentAmount,
 subrogation.TotalRecoveryAmt,
 subrogation.FirstDueDate,
 subrogation.SubrogationProviderNo,
 subrogation.ResponsiblePartyIntlInd,
 subrogation.ResponsibleOwnerIntlInd,
 subrogation.AdverseCarrierInternationalInd,
 subrogation.Demand,
 subrogation.RowId,
 subrogation.SubrogationProviderName,
 subrogation.SubrogationAmountPaid,
 subrogation.NetRecovery,
 subrogation.SubrogationAmountCollected,
 subrogation.SubrogationNetPaid
from subrogation 
where CMMContainer='Claim'
